<li><a href="/wiki/John_Bodkin_Adams" title="John Bodkin Adams">Dr John Bodkin Adams</a> — British general practitioner and suspected serial killer who "possibly provided the role model for Shipman".<sup id="cite_ref-39" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-39" title=""><span>[</span>40<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Michael_Swango" title="Michael Swango">Michael Swango</a> — American surgeon and serial killer</li>
