<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.strangerinblood.co.uk/html/case.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.strangerinblood.co.uk/html/case.htm" rel="nofollow">Strangerinblood.co.uk</a> <a href="/wiki/Nigel_Cox_(doctor)" title="Nigel Cox (doctor)">Dr Nigel Cox</a> was convicted of only attempted murder in 1992, in the death of Lillian Boyes.</li>
